Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.20,0:02:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護江戶的強力結界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三角陣之中的寬永寺\N在上野戰爭時遭到破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而失去了一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.94,0:02:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來掌管寬永寺靈力的\N是北斗之龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.64,0:02:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以寺內最東北方的\N德川家靈廟為頭的龍之佈陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要完全重生那個三角陣\N是不可能的 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許可以在某種程度內\N做好應急的措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想用本尊的砂子來代替水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個水泉算是龍的喉嚨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以滋潤一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.37,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍頭與喉嚨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有手與腳都有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣脈之道萬無一失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.01,0:03:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下來的是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後就是心臟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好重的霉味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.95,0:03:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是名人\N左甚五郎創作的吞水之龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以這頭龍為本尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當做北斗之陣的心臟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九十四話\N風與水的輓歌  現在！使盡全力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.11,0:03:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（咒）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍脈馬上就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 那是玉座之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有夠誇張的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.19,0:04:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想藉由玉座之陣操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.19,0:04:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以中禪寺湖\N為中心的巨大五芒星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來改變龍脈的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.16,0:04:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破了這個陣\N阻止他們的陰謀以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍脈會怎麼走呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日光是靈場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要方向不改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那自淨作用就會發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使龍脈自己消散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然找上這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個…難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大陸風水 剛壁之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水大人 式神們都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我讓他們當基石了\N他們不會不滿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好衝進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有風水師能越過這個結界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.37,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在 風與水要做一了結了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我若是死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的麻煩你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是陣風嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！辛苦你們了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我們盡力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題是到底能發揮多少功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能會不及原來的一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 搞不好三成都不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一線希望\N果然在緋村他們身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元老院嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.05,0:06:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算他們是收賄賂的貪官\N我也不能見死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.67,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被這個國家放逐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.95,0:07:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡海到大陸的我們一族\N不知嘗過多少辛酸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.18,0:07:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被政府徵用是一時運氣罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你們把恨意瞄準風之一族\N就是恨錯人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風之一族也付出巨大犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受傷的人不是只有你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不聽 去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想請你回答一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:08:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙 元老院的人\N他們值得救嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這跟價值沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是人渣 人還是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.18,0:08:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護人民是警察的義務\N不能混入私情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有個好主意\N讓我幫助你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就洗耳恭聽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是人渣 人還是人嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風與水的力量不分上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.71,0:08:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 勝利機會就在\N豁出生命的人那邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大和風水 鳳凰之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不珍惜自己的命嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了達成\N我們水之一族的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何人都不准打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.83,0:09:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狼牙之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 快趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.09,0:09:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道\N風水不會這樣就毀滅的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果毀滅是天與地的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會樂意接受！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.91,0:09:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔 你贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.44,0:10:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玉座之陣完全毀滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.11,0:10:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.65,0:10:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.62,0:10:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝利機會就在\N豁出生命的人那邊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 你說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.03,0:10:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水之一族永遠不會毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且君臨這個國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玉座之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再生了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准你們輕視我們的志氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是為了這一天而活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水之一族繼續活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我繼續活下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.84,0:11:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是風水師呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想跟大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟時間一起活下去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是靈水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為偉大的水之一族族長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後還是完成了那個使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.86,0:11:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈水大人\N把自己獻給玉座之陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了操作龍脈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓自己被附身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玉座之陣現在依然健在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道真的要完了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.69,0:12:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把翡翠紋章交出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊藤博文大人抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,井上馨大人抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警視廳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們要求停止會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？為什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是不知道理由呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察做事這麼蠻橫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川路大人 請你們回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這樣求你還不行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您的理由太不清楚了 請回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,署長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.04,0:12:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翡翠紋章？\N我不懂你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙確實可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.09,0:13:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是東照宮移走的\N機關的本體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是堀田老頭說的東西啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.86,0:13:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翡翠紋章確實在我手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有這個紋章\N我才不需要靈水的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.73,0:14:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後我就可以\N自由自在操縱龍脈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佐伯從神佛分離令的資料中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道翡翠紋章的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而從陽明門把紋章盜走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.65,0:14:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是他沒告訴靈水這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.52,0:14:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果知道有這東西\N靈水就不需要犧牲自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.99,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他拿著翡翠紋章\N還坐視靈水死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是為了水之一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是為了讓他自己\N控制這個國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經沒辦法\N阻止向府內而去的龍脈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 破壞碉堡上的石敢當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一口氣解放內部的氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用翡翠紋章的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撞上先行的龍脈 或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之試試看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.29,0:14:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間考慮了 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.46,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？是炮擊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位請盡速避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬人拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你跟風水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.86,0:15:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是德川時代留下的殘影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要成為光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為新時代的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.27,0:15:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有人來不及逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是最後的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裏面沒人 都確認過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.88,0:15:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疏導避難完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個戰略不錯\N可是有點過火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是被曉得\N可不是免職就了事的 真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賭賭看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寬永寺附近的避難命令呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.74,0:16:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 傳佈下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也要回去寬永寺\N看結界陣的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能做的都做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.39,0:16:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的\N就看北斗之陣能撐多久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託…\N保護住東京…這個城市吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紋章啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守住石敢當吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變了！我變了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從得到這個紋章以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有事物都以我為中心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.01,0:17:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有它\N龍脈就在我掌控下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.95,0:17:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是這世界的光明\N光明就是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算被魔所附
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也決不可能成為光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天地人的聖靈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請保佑他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,螺旋的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.52,0:17:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風 接住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧 方向是辰己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,粉碎龍脈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.84,0:18:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 只是減弱而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.14,0:18:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經…無法挽救了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像停下來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個看就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是緋村他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.09,0:19:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,川路長官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.32,0:19:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,津南不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必管他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去元老院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光明…消失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,備中守大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.89,0:19:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寬永寺的北斗之陣\N太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次的事…是我對江戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.46,0:20:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是我對東京最後的貢獻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是人不該擁有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.40,0:20:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它埋在武藏野的泉底吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後東京就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.34,0:20:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 這個國家就麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 只要我活著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前任寺社官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堀田備中守 正睦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是那個老人的來歷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.66,0:20:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寺社官啊…怪不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.47,0:20:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這件事\N你們報紙沒有刊載啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.20,0:20:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.97,0:20:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是貪官被捕的消息\N刊得很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是佐伯自己供出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.24,0:20:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也只是冰山的一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過川路的\N契而不捨倒是值得稱讚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.65,0:21:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到\N你會稱讚警視廳的頭目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.29,0:21:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥 快點幫忙晾衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別發呆 別發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.79,0:21:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛找我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 要晾了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不習慣被人送行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.95,0:21:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代我向大家問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.45,0:21:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陣風 這次的事幸虧有你\N我想向你鄭重道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.72,0:21:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到幫助的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我一個人的話\N是什麼也幹不出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.03,0:21:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老實說 遇見你\N我的心塌實多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.30,0:21:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許我們走的路只是影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今知道自己不是孤獨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.81,0:21:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少可以成為活下去的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.58,0:22:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風水是自然之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.62,0:22:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風水師\N必需與自然共同活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順由天與地的意志…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.15,0:22:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們一同走下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走完自己的道路

